Now when it comes to licensing, this is when things get interesting. Let me explain.

- The Hugo framework itself is licensed under Apache-2.0.
- Giscus, the comments service I use, is licensed under MIT.
- PaperMod, the template I used is also licensed under MIT.
- The content on my website is generally licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International. Any content that is not licensed under this or is "All Rights Reserved" will be clearly labelled as such.
